212252</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cdafb8f9bc8c1f4db3ac8de34fc1d831b0d1c39d","tid":1211830,"uid":157802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:26:58.000Z","msg":"其實真係好感動。<br />\n早上同其他人都係著黑衫係立會抗爭，因為訊號唔好，完全唔知出面既狀况，一直以為只有一小部份人。<br />\n點知中午休息行出去，居然有一片白色人潮，感覺就好似佢地保護我地唔俾狗包夾咁。<br />\n衝就我地，守就你地。"},{"pid":"95a334f40a9c0591ce6cafdbb586bdd2103517a3","tid":1211830,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:28:52.000Z","msg":"部落 + 聯盟 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;燃燒軍團<br />\n<br />\n少d內戰 一齊對付左勁敵先！"},{"pid":"533bb1abb6e6b45dfd880b9dca889c55efef7ebb","tid":1211830,"uid":47509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:29:08.000Z","msg":"因為所有人目標只有一個 加油堅持呀"},{"pid":"8d77dae3604d5d0a3ecf30e03c83343fdb2d0324","tid":1211830,"uid":34698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:31:13.000Z","msg":"香港而家只係分 有腦同無腦"},{"pid":"11ee50f4f09ec6df62d7ecf0d29f8673d24a208a","tid":1211830,"uid":36104,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"21f5a4792f21ec85f77330f31972716541c0a887","tid":1211830,"uid":124630,"like":394,"dislike":2,"score":392,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"我一直都信香港人唔係咁自私自利，只係因為社會氛圍同歸邊文化整到大家互相對立，冇咗互信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次係個機會俾香港人重新團結，睇住大家由互屌到和理勇武合作，唔係話咁樣一定贏硬，但比單打獨鬥一定好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n場仗仲未完，希望大家可以keep住團火對準班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:32:01.000Z","msg":"其實係支那刻意分化香港人<br />\n以前邊會睇得錢咁重<br />\n士多見我冇乜錢買野食都會請/平畀我<br />\n點會咁撚閪，加價加到離曬譜<br />\n因為濕鳩鋪租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋大量支那種<br />\n佢地係冇人性一群<br />\n我地為左防佢地<br />\n防曬全世界，包括有人性嘅人"},{"pid":"e2fc3d2194a780c7ab02e2886c95aa74428ddb7f","tid":1211830,"uid":131621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:35:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"95e1b6a6e95a9b4be9fab11924f230375e7c0e8a","tid":1211830,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ef98d53ac8023c4f8f5648a6ad96ca6085c05d2","tid":1211830,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"從前 連登仔鐘意乜都批鬥<br />\n見到議員 就會屌柒佢地政棍<br />\n但鄺議員成晚不斷走結果攰到暈低<br />\n而楊議員仲落金鐘幫後生仔去挑機<br />\n<br />\n見港女就話人係雞係公廁<br />\n而最近好多港女都選擇做前線<br />\n<br />\n見到仔就話人金鐘肥矮柒毒<br />\n而今日好多巴打都選擇守護住香港<br />\n<br />\n見耶撚就會屌耶撚on9煩膠<br />\n但耶撚選擇左保護一班義士<br />\n<br />\n見到南亞裔人士就屌佢地得閒就捉d女黎女女女<br />\n但佢地選擇同香港人一齊守護呢個城市<br />\n<br />\n見到的士就會屌dc9無禮貌<br />\n但今日dc9一野撞左落部狗車度<br />\n<br />\n慢慢發現 原來香港係可以共融<br />\n只要大家目標一致 槍口對外<br />\n其實香港 仲有好多值得大家鐘意嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:46:00.000Z","msg":"你講一講又好似係"},{"pid":"6a2ec7af3ad31de140a754950e23cf5d43a0ced5","tid":1211830,"uid":119458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"53d41691e58f7318382880f835677e5922152ecc","tid":1211830,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XK3BvOT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXK3BvOT.png&h=a0b6c78a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dAkc2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dAkc2e.png&h=99c6a4e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:49:17.000Z","msg":"名又唔blur，人地得罪你乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家被記名點相嗰個係你定佢"},{"pid":"d26907e8457c804364f4993982b3576160c67926","tid":1211830,"uid":20908,"like":0,"disl