/>\n其實香港 仲有好多值得大家鐘意嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"屌，睇到想喊"}]}